{"tid":1114573,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(急) intern vs summer school","createTime":"2019-04-18T13:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T13:24:56.000Z","uid":223780,"like":39,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"37fe3f9e757097f986b9260452493170b4d817b0","tid":1114573,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:58:53.000Z","msg":"首先講下背景<br />\n乞食科yr2<br />\n<br />\n一早apply左yr3 3至6月sem2去澳洲exchange <br />\n下年咁遲先返香港驚apply唔到所以諗住今年做定intern廢事一個都冇做就grad<br />\n點知major突然間話去佢哋有聯繫嘅u讀summer school 返嚟可以trans cred<br />\n不過要year2 去先有得trans<br />\n好驚去完澳洲冇cred trans 到返嚟（嗰邊間ud course outline講左等於冇講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爆cred試過但搞到失眠免得過都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n如果去嘅話至少可以compensate一個course<br />\n同埋真係想去<br />\n貪得意apply左summer school scholarship 中左5000（所有洗費要20000）<br />\n成世未拎過scholarship <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但intern如果今個暑假唔做下年人喺澳洲<br />\n未必間間公司肯video in<br />\n就算肯都可能有輸蝕<br />\n如果最後0intern grad好驚乞食<br />\n<br />\n所以想問下大家有乜睇法<br />\n同埋聽講winter internship 少好多公司揀<br />\n有冇巴絲有經驗可以分享下⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />intern <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />summer school"},{"pid":"b7f0176a643c6f1600c85b4445d18c6be0b32398","tid":1114573,"uid":99243,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T14:05:51.000Z","msg":"還掂year 3都去exchange 啦，year 2 咪留喺香港返intern囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n0 intern 真喺好輸蝕架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c233850ca0a0ab53d9a44b7993fa1de3dc71ebc","tid":1114573,"uid":91813,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T14:28:37.000Z","msg":"開心就summer school<br />\n前途就intern"},{"pid":"525a1516dfee23798e1af7780c8bc7b8dc0ebf6a","tid":1114573,"uid":223780,"like":0,"d